Name: Calvin Castlebrook
Abilities:
- Advanced swordsmanship
- Flight
- Speed boost (limited to durations of around 15-20 seconds at a time)
- Can open Dark Fountains
- Extreme regeneration factor
- Pigeon-sense (enhanced awareness and reflexes)
Weapons:
- Terra Blade
  * Sword beam summoning/manipulation
  * Sword slash summoning/manipulation
- Dark's Tizona 
  * Emits light
  * Inflicts Lunar Blood debuff - drains away enemy's lifestat
